{"tid":2151851,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"（求救）地盤散工被拖糧","createTime":"2020-08-11T15:13:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T17:59:02.000Z","uid":329218,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dbf170404901cd15874ef53c0fffb6c474937803","tid":2151851,"uid":329218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:13:31.000Z","msg":"【代post】<br />\n7月尾係日出康城第七期（中國建築）返左兩日散工，有5個工人中途被炒（無原因），於是追出糧。到宜家，仲有兩名工人未有糧出。對上判頭態度極為惡劣，以種種藉口推遲出糧，亦曾聲稱出左糧但傳來發票的戶口號碼是錯的，或者根本不是當事人的名字，有欺詐之嫌疑。最近一次話無錢，要優先出糧比其他工人人，總之已經令事主心力交瘁。<br />\n<br />\n打過去勞工處，但係由於唔知道對方全名，所以告唔到，淨係有whatsapp。有無人會識果度嘅人，或者知道應該點樣可以追翻條數？"},{"pid":"afefe38002273e27b2418b435455d5e5380b4622","tid":2151851,"uid":343239,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:15:44.000Z","msg":"下次小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d8bd0f9f759c20f9c0a9555fc77f0eb0941201","tid":2151851,"uid":329218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afefe38002273e27b2418b435455d5e5380b4622","tid":2151851,"uid":343239,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:15:44.000Z","msg":"下次小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:17:19.000Z","msg":"事主做地盤散工做左十幾年都係第一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629366bb970708c74c509294c0db6302bc49bd68","tid":2151851,"uid":343239,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"28d8bd0f9f759c20f9c0a9555fc77f0eb0941201","tid":2151851,"uid":329218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afefe38002273e27b2418b435455d5e5380b4622","tid":2151851,"uid":343239,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:15:44.000Z","msg":"下次小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:17:19.000Z","msg":"事主做地盤散工做左十幾年都係第一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15